OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThousands complain to HMRC 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fabout tax repayments       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of people complaining to His
OL,6, Majesty's Revenue and Customs about    
OL,7, companies claiming tax repayments on   
OL,8, their behalf has more than tripled in  
OL,9, two years, a Money Box investigation   
OL,10, has discovered.                        
OL,12,FMany say this is happening without     
OL,13,Ftheir knowledge or permission.         
OL,15,FHMRC admits there are significant      
OL,16,Fconcerns about repayment agents and is 
OL,17,F"considering its next steps".          
OL,19,FThe complaints are about what are      
OL,20,Fcalled "deeds of assignment".          
